        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Child Care Funds Accountability Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Health and Human Services to monitor and report on compliance with the use of funds for the child care stabilization grants and the Child Care and Development Block Grant program provided by the American Rescue Plan Act of 2021.</p>]]>
        </text>
